file_content.text: They've got anti-air cannons on that island. Hope you appreciate what I'm doing for you here!
Been told you need a good ship. Well, I don't have a good ship. I have a great ship!
Heard they don't like visitors where you're headed. I'll take you as close as I can, but I'm not dying!
